    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA333-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu poruḷvayiṉ piriviṉkaṇ āṟṟāḷākiya talaimakaḷait tōḻi vaṟpuṟuttatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is how the confidante encouraged HER who wasn’t able to bear it during the separation for the sake of wealth.</p>
        </div>
      <div xml:id="NA333">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            maḻaitoḻi luḻantu māvicum pukanteṉak</l>
<l>            kaḻaikavi ṉaḻinta kallatarc ciṟuneṟip</l>
<l>            paralava lūṟaṟ ciṟunīr maruṅkiṟ</l>
<l>            pūnutal yāṉaiyoṭu puliporu tuṇṇuñ</l>
<l>            curaṉiṟan tariya veṉṉā ruraṉaḻin</l>
<l>            tuṇmali neñcamoṭu vaṇmai vēṇṭi</l>
<l>            yarumporuṭ kakaṉṟa kātalar muyakketirntu</l>
<l>            tiruntiḻaip paṇaittōḷ peṟunar pōlu</l>
<l>            nīṅkuka mātōniṉ ṉavala mōṅkumicai</l>
<l>            yuyarpukaḻ nalli loṇcuvarp porunti</l>
<l>            nayavaru kurala palli</l>
<l>            naḷḷeṉ yāmat tuḷḷutoṟum paṭumē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>            The lover who departed for difficult wealth,</l>
<l rend="indent">            wishing to be generous, with a heart full inside, strength perishing,</l>
<l rend="indent4">            not saying</l>
<l rend="indent4">            “difficult to traverse<note place="foot">Actually, the absolutive <term xml:lang="ta">iṟantu</term> is impossible here; the construction clearly demands an infinitive or a verbal noun.</note> [are] the deserts,”</l>
<l rend="indent">            where the tiger eats, having fought the elephant with flower-forehead</l>
<l rend="indent2">            by the side of a little water oozing from the pebbly depression</l>
<l rend="indent3">            on the stony sandy small path where the bamboo’s beauty is perished,</l>
<l rend="indent4">            because the clouds have ascended the great sky, task finished,</l>
<l rend="indent4">            – meeting [her] with an embrace,</l>
<l>        he will obtain the bamboo shoulder with perfect jewels, it seems.</l>
<l>        May not your affliction leave?</l>
<l>        The gecko with a voice from which longing comes,</l>
<l rend="indent">            joining the bright wall in the highly praised good house</l>
<l rend="indent">            on the high elevation,</l>
<l>        falls in whenever it remembers at deep midnight.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
